{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"92e130a579","title":"中共新都县委关于刘亚平同志错划右派的改正通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"99168a9bd5","index":0,"year":1979,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"92e130a579"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"733821e0d9","type":"title","text":"中共新都县委关于刘亚平同志错划右派的改正通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"617f852f2c","type":"appellation","text":"关于刘亚平同志错划右派的改正通知","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"96471777d7","type":"paragraph","text":"刘亚平同志原在新都师范附小任教，1958年划为右派。根据中共中央〈1978〉55号文件和1957年《中共中央关于“划分右派分子的标准”的通知》精神，经县委摘帽领导小组1979年3月17日会议研究决定：刘亚平同志属于错划，应予改正，撤销原划右派的处分决定，恢复政治名誉，恢复公职，恢复原工资小教行政五级，工资从1978年10月开始计发。对家属、子女档案中有关右派材料，要抽出销毁。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"2c2c3083ec","type":"paragraph","text":"特此通知","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"2e6cf1196a","type":"appellation","text":"中共新都县委","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"fbd6e33ef9","type":"appellation","text":"1979年3月17日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"c7cd0eb86e","type":"appellation","text":"主送：文教局；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"},{"id":"4d45d1d983","type":"appellation","text":"抄送：成都市金牛区委摘帽办，组织部、宣传部、文教局；县委组织部、宣传部、统战部、公安局。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579"}],"page":{"id":"11ddada291","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92e130a579","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}